Description: Custom ordered John Cruz 1959 Stratocaster Relic completed in October 2006 for Wild West Guitars. An early example of John's legendary work and, in particular, his incredible relic work. Guitar is in mint/unplayed condition and is as it was when it left John Cruz's workbench and the Fender Custom Shop back in 2006 (other than a string change that I did a few years ago since it had been sitting in the case all of it's life). Guitar also comes with it's original tweed case and every piece of case candy that it came with including the COA, a 3-way switch and more (see pics). P/U SET PICKUP STRAT TEX SPCL CUST PICKUP STRAT TEX SPCL CUST RWRP PICKUP STRAT TEX SPCL CUST PG PARCHMENT 1 ply SWITCH 5-WAY A truly beautiful, incredible and collectible guitar custom built by the one and only John Cruz.
